name: UNCEASING VIXENS 13:55
description: An interlaced vision of everlasting beauty. Unceasing Vixens tangled with a collective aura of an intimate overture. Silently singing the sounds of the sirens, with an overwhelming verse. The melody of a voluptuous ballad meant to lure you in. Their poetic aria ringing in the unconscious mind. They direct wisdom of magnificent passion. Glorious moments created for a sublime future. A promise of a better tomorrow. Adulation as a keepsake for an otherwise lost heart. Though not heavenly in nature, they are most undoubtedly quintessential in growing your character. Your inner child will forever be captivated by these exquisite creatures.
